@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : searchRoutes(origin, destination)
activate System

note right of System: The system searches for routes\nmatching the given origin, destination,\nor both. All parameters are optional.

System --> ATCC : informs operation success and returns list of matching routes
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml
